# .trivyignore — Trivy vulnerability ignore file
#
# Zero-tolerance policy: every entry here MUST include owner, reason, and expiry.
# Expired entries will be removed during periodic review.
#
# Format:
#   # owner: <name> | reason: <justification> | expires: YYYY-MM-DD
#   CVE-XXXX-XXXXX
#
# Example:
#   # owner: security-team | reason: not reachable in our stack | expires: 2026-06-01
#   CVE-2026-12345

